ining sauce and garnish with fresh watercress."}],"hintsAndTricks":["<strong>Nutritional comments<\/strong>: This menu is very balanced and complete and can be combined with a dessert made with fresh seasonal fruit.","You can cook this recipe with other fish (bream, hake, etc.)."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","30m","2 portions"]}